quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Baravuze bamwe badatinya guhura natwe bati:- nikuki twebwe tutamanurirwa Abamarayika canke ngo tubone Umuremyi wacu? Ntankeka barihayagije mumitima yabo nukwidohora kumwe kuniniya cane"
  25,22,"Umusi bazobona Abamarayika kuri uwo musi, ntamunezero uzoba uhari ku bantu bagize ivyaha kuko bazovuga bati:- Imana yobirenza kure ibi bihano bitwegereye"
  25,23,Natwe tuzogendera kuvyo bakoze mubikorwa vyabo hanyuma tubigire nk’inkungugu zasanzajwe
  25,24,Abantu bo mw’ijuru kuri uwo musi bazoba bari mubwicaro bwiza n’ahantu hukwinezereza heza
  25,25,N’umusi Amajuru azosatagurika hanyuma hazemwo ibicu bizo manukiramwo Abamarayika benshi cane
  25,26,"Ubwami bw’ukuri kuri uwo musi buzoba ari bwanyene imigisha, kandi uwo musi uzoba ari umusi ugoye cane ku bantu batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  25,27,"No k’umusi w’uwahemukiye umutima wiwe azokwirya amaboko yiwe avuga ati:- iyo nkurikira inzira y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Muhammadi (aui)"
  25,28,Eh! iyo ntagira naka ngo abe ariwe umugenzi wanje
  25,29,"Niwe yantakaje nca ndareka gukurikira ubutumwa bw’Imana bumaze kunshikira, mu vy’ukuri Shetani ita umuntu mukaga"
  25,30,"N’intumwa y’Imana yama ivuga iti:- Muremyi wanje, mu vy’ukuri abantu banje bagize iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu nk’ikintu cahunzwe"
  25,31,"Uku rero niko twagiriye intumwa z’Imana zose ubwansi bw’abantu babi, n’Umuremyi wawe arahagije kuba indongozi n’umufasha"
  25,32,"Baravuze bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bati:- ni kuki atamanuriwe iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu icarimwe nk’uku imeze kugira ngo dutsimbataze umutima wawe kandi tukaba twayitondesheje kurutonde rwiza"
  25,33,Kandi ntibazo kuzanira akarorero akariko kose mugabo tuzo kuzanira ukuri kwama hamwe n’insiguro itomoye neza
  25,34,"Abazo kwegeranywa bubitse inda zabo hasi, bagashikanwa mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu, abo bantu bazoba ahantu habi cane nukuba barataye inzira y’ukuri"
  25,35,Ntankeka twaramuhaye intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) igitabu duca tumushira hamwe na musaza wiwe Haruna (iii) kuba muba shikiranganji biwe
  25,36,"Duca tubabwira ngo bagende ku bantu bahakanye amajambo yacu matagatifu, natwe duca turabahonya ukuri kwama"
  25,37,"N’abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) mugihe bahakana intumwa z’Imana twaciye tubibiza mumazi nukubagira ibitekerezo ku bantu bose, kandi twarabateguriye abahemukiye imitima yabo ibihano bibabaza cane"
  25,38,"Nabene Aadi hamwe na Thamuda, hamwe n’abantu bo mubinogo hamwe n’imvukira nyinshi zaho zari muribo"
  25,39,Bose twarabagiriyeko uburorero nabose uko bangana twarabahoneje bimwe vy’akarorero
  25,40,"Mu vy’ukuri barashitse kw’Isi yamanuriweko imvura mbi cane, mbega ntibayibona, ahubwo ntibemera yuko hariho ukuzurwa kw’abantu"
  25,41,"Bakubonye ntakindi bagira atari ukujajura gusa nukuvuga bati:- mbega iyi niyo Mana yarungitse ngo ibe intumwa y’Imana"
  25,42,"Mu vy’ukuri yari hafi yukutuzimiza kubera Imana zacu iyo tutigumya kuribo, kuko ubu vuba bari hafi yukumenya igihe bazobona ibihano vyuwahe yazimiye agata inzira"
  25,43,"Mbega wamubonye umwe yikunze gusumba ibindi vyose kuba ariyo Mana yiwe, mbega woshobora kumukingira"
  25,44,"Canke wiyumvira yuko benshi muribo bumva canke bategera? Ntibari abo nuko bari bameze nk’ibikoko, ahubwo bari bazimiye inzira gusumba ibindi vyose"
  25,45,"Mbega ntiwabonye Umuremyi wawe ingene yasanzaje igitutu, iyo ibishaka ntankeka yarikukigira ngo kigume hamwe gusa, hanyuma tugira izuba ngo ribe icemezo kuriryo"
  25,46,Hanyuma tugikwegera iwacu buhoro buhoro
  25,47,"Nayo\tniyo\tyabagiriye\tijoro\tkuba\tari\timpuzu,\tn’itiro\tkuba\tnk’urupfu, nukugira umutaga kuba nk’ukuzuka"
  25,48,"Nayo niyo irungika imiyaga kuba ari inkuru nziza imbere y’imigisha yayo, nukumanura amazi meza avuye mubicu"
  25,49,"Kugira ngo tuzure Isi yari yarapfuye, nuku nyweshereza kuri\tbamwe twaremye haba mubikoko n’abantu benshi"
  25,50,"Mu vy’ukuri twarayigabuye kuribo kugira ngo abantu bibuke, mugabo benshi muribo barahakanye atari ukugereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu gusa"
  25,51,"Iyo\tdushaka\ttwari\tkubarungikira\tmugisagara\tkimwe\tkukindi\tumuntu abatuza"
  25,52,"Rero\tntugamburukire\tabahakanyi\tb’Imana\tyabo\ty’ukuri,\tahubwo nuhiganwe nabo kuri iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu kwihiganwa rininiya cane"